# 🔐 Hand Gesture Lock System

## 📌 Overview

The **Hand Gesture Lock System** is an AI-based security application that uses hand gestures as a password mechanism. Instead of traditional PINs or patterns, users can unlock the system using predefined hand gestures detected through a camera.

---

## 🚀 Features

* ✋ Gesture-based authentication
* 🎥 Real-time hand tracking using webcam
* 🔒 Secure and user-friendly locking system
* ⚡ Fast and efficient gesture recognition
* 🤖 Built using AI/ML concepts

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* Python 🐍
* OpenCV 👁️
* MediaPipe ✋
* NumPy 📊

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
Hand-Gesture-Lock/
│── main.py
│── utils/
│── models/
│── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```
git clone https://github.com/Charangujjula/Hand_gesture_lock.git
```

2. Navigate to the project folder:

```
cd Hand_gesture_lock
```

3. Install required dependencies:

```
pip install opencv-python mediapipe numpy
```

---

## ▶️ How to Run

Run the main file:

```
python main.py
```

* Show your predefined gesture in front of the camera
* System will recognize and unlock if matched

---

